    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Comparison of juvenile RVs of Gryphaea, Nanogyra, and Actinostreon. 1. Gryphaea ferruginea Terquem, 1855, Aalenian, Poland (redrawn after Pugaczewska 1971 b, fig. 1). 2. Nanogyra (Palaeogyra) virgula (Deshayes, 1831), Upper Kimmeridgian, Switzerland. 3. Nanogyra (N.) nana (J. Sowerby, 1822), Lower Kimmeridgian, Switzerland. 4. Actinostreon marshii (J. Sowerby, 1814), Callovian, Lithuania." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/288043/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

